column3:
<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
The enthusiastic observer needs help retrieving lost plants.
Deliver the tufts of cloud mallow to the enthusiastic observer.
What a sight! An ampelos sneezed and sent tufts of cloud mallow flying every which way.
But while highly amusing, I'll never be able to gather them all up alone...unless you're willing to lend a hand?
Thank you so much! Let's split up and start looking for them.
Be on the lookout for fluffy white plants floating around Poieten Oikos, and bring any you find back here.
Did you find any of the plants?
Perfect! It's such a relief to have them back...
A somewhat amateur creator invented the concept to bring more life into the clouds. Which is all well and good, but they get blown away far too easily.
It would be nice if they were a bit more wind resistant... We need to know they can settle in a place without fear of them flying off because some beast breathed on them too hard.
Well, I'd better put them back where they belong before a light breeze undoes all your hard work. Here, take this as thanks for your help.
